    "In terms of the content, ChatGPT usually proposes concepts connected with time travel and includes something magical in the answer, irrespective of the genre.",
    "It can also solve riddles and decipher secret signs, codes, treasure maps or journals.",
    "However, the chatbots cannot be specific, and their answers may be only taken as inspiration and further research and exploration.",
    "For example, in the detective story, ChatGPT provided us with some historical clues from the Middle Ages to elaborate the story and boost the creative writing process.",
    "The chatbot can also help to decide between two or more plot twists and even explain what will happen if this concrete concept is chosen (Table 1, Story 3)."
